Stock image providers
----------------------
The editor's optional stock-image integration fetches images at runtime using
an API key that YOU configure. Lit Pigeon does not bundle any provider content.
When you enable these, you are responsible for following each provider's
attribution and usage terms:

- Unsplash — https://unsplash.com  (Unsplash API Terms: attribution and
  download/UTM tracking requirements apply)
- Pexels — https://www.pexels.com  (Pexels API Guidelines: attribution applies)
